const errorCodes = {
    DEFAULT: 'Oops!  Something went wrong. Please try again later!!',
    ID_NOT_KNOWN: 'Unknown User ID!!',
    ID_UNAVAILABLE: 'User ID Unavailable!!',
    DUPLICATE_USERNAME: 'Username already exists!!',
    UNAUTHORIZED_LOGIN: 'Unauthorized Access!!',
    NON_EXISTENT_MEETUP: 'Meetup no more exists!!',
    USERNAME_MANDATORY: 'Please fill in the username!!',
    LOGIN_MANDATORY: 'Please login in your account!!',
    REGISTRATION_MANDATORY: 'Please register to use services!!',
    NETWORK_ERROR: 'Problem connecting to your network!!',
    FIRSTNAME_MANDATORY: 'Please fill in your first name',
    LASTNAME_MANDATORY: 'Please fill in your first name'
  };
  
  export default errorCodes;
